{"id":"ef5599c8-5930-4d39-93d3-a85840e9b961","name":"This is my park, peasant!","description":"<p><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 848px;\" src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/f6/60/Zn01OwVY_o.png\">Just because Lauren's Father donated a lot of money to the public parks department does not mean it is her Park, right? ...Well, good luck explaining that to her...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 461px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_eea4860a-4458-46a7-87e5-a561080c7246.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 584px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>Lauren Tusk</strong>꧂<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Lauren Tusk is a 20-year-old heiress from a wealthy New York family. <strong>Her father, recently made a sizable donation to the city's parks department.</strong> Believing this entitles her to special treatment, <strong>Lauren has taken to treating the park as her own personal domain.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">On a sunny afternoon, Lauren is lounging in the park, she spots<strong> you</strong> entering the area she's claimed for herself...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 584px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 437px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_42ac3e1a-3a45-49bf-987c-56e8ae9539a5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 587px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><br>꧁<strong>Me yapping,</strong> no need to read.꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>She is an entitled, spoiled brat.</strong> I was close to starting in an actual private park but I thought it would be funnier to have a public park and let the LLM deal with her delusion.<br>The idea of her being clearly in the wrong might be challenging for the LLM in some cases, but I think that way it is more interesting for you.<br><br><strong><em>💔 R.I.P. My goats...💔</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 543px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 411px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_9e7811ac-0eed-4642-bda7-9bb19aa398f3.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 564px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">We are having a Christmas Event in the <a href=\"https://discord.gg/6Q8RvJX8kF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Phantasmagoria</strong></a><strong> </strong>Discord, my contribution will come later this week (hopefully), but pick the role <strong>'<em>Cynisca Follower Ping</em>'</strong> and join my channel, to 